Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.52,0:00:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.55,0:00:09.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We received the power of the Legendary Dragon from the Duel Monsters World.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.18,0:00:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't believe it, but that wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.39,0:00:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A powerful Monster has revealed itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.31,0:00:18.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's what is trying to destroy the world?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.93,0:00:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though the Legendary Dragon, Timaeus's power was able to stop it,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.39,0:00:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the fight has just begun!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.29,0:00:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.25,0:00:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.55,0:01:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.81,0:01:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.27,0:01:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.28,0:01:22.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.21,0:01:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.30,0:01:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:02:00.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Invitation From Pegasus"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:09.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After the Duel Monsters sightings that occurred yesterday,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}there have been many abnormal incidents, like auroras or massive tornadoes, happening around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:20.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We experienced auroras\Nand large tornadoes ourselves last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.42,0:02:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Some even claim to have witnessed "Monsters" in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.79,0:02:26.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So what happened last night {\i1}wasn't{\i0} just a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.36,0:02:33.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because we still have the card you got from the Duel Monsters World.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.54,0:02:38.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how you look at it, it's just like any normal card.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.45,0:02:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see any great power\N in it or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better be careful with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an important card given to the True Duelists.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:49.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mhm-hmm. I got something unbelievable.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.79,0:02:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The power to\N save the world from despair...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monocle of Timaeus...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.49,0:03:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what are you gonna do now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"What," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.12,0:03:07.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no clues\Nabout the enemies at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know where the ones who stole Yugi's God Cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.95,0:03:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those "Musketeers of Doma" guys have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.66,0:03:15.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on~!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get any of this~
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.32,0:03:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.99,0:03:27.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anything\Nwe can use as clues?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.26,0:03:30.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like, say, you rub the thing and it goes "PUFF!" all of a sudden!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell us\N where the enemies went?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.09,0:03:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.72,0:03:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you say\N we need to be careful with it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.32,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just trying it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.99,0:03:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:42.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell...?\NIt's so loud up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.16,0:03:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.99,0:03:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yugi, a parcel came for you today from America.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.14,0:03:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be from Otogi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.25,0:03:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, he's in America right now, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.02,0:04:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.72,0:04:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see... "Industrial Illusions"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,WHAT DID YOU SAY?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Industrial Illusions is the company that Pegasus owns, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.45,0:04:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides this card..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.92,0:04:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a video letter along with it...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.71,0:04:23.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't the same thing happen before Duelist Kingdom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.49,0:04:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Grandpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.45,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honda-{\i0}kun{\i1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Anzu!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.96,0:04:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can get in the way now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.37,0:04:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shall we begin...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:39.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is this a Dark Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.63,0:04:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My power is the Dark Power of the Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.42,0:04:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Millennium Eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.13,0:04:46.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll see you again at the Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.89,0:04:50.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you want back your most valuable treasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.73,0:05:03.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.22,0:05:08.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't we be better off\N throwing this out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.09,0:05:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Pegasus doesn't have\Nthe Millennium Eye anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.87,0:05:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't that make it alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.20,0:05:14.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.39,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was stolen by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.02,0:05:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.39,0:05:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Although he doesn't have it now,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus was the one chosen by the Millennium Eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.38,0:05:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And he's also the one who created Duel Monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.35,0:05:33.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe this tape\Nhas something to do with this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.22,0:05:34.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.35,0:05:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's very likely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.12,0:05:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we check it out?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.75,0:05:40.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oi, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not ready to die yet, ya know!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.46,0:05:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Long time no see... Yugi boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.49,0:05:52.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He appeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.70,0:05:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I know this is abrupt,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:58.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but you should know what's happening around the world right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.37,0:05:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.42,0:06:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like an ordinary video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.66,0:06:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Duel Monsters is the game I created.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.92,0:06:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And now these Monsters\Nare being substantiated,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.59,0:06:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and have caused a lot or panic around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just what has happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.55,0:06:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've done some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.52,0:06:19.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And I realized one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.79,0:06:21.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What has he realized?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.94,0:06:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About this thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:28.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to talk to Yugi boy personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.07,0:06:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.03,0:06:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, I cannot leave this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am being watched by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To be completely honest, I am taking a gamble on whether or not this letter even reaches you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.24,0:06:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But if you safely get it,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.70,0:06:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}please take the card with you and come to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.34,0:06:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will arrange for a plane to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.55,0:06:54.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So please make haste!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.05,0:06:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will wait for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.17,0:06:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.21,0:07:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have no choice but to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.24,0:07:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We don't have any other clues or leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.52,0:07:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.71,0:07:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.54,0:07:12.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:14.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't waste your time here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.41,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.97,0:07:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.57,0:07:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you go alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.31,0:07:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.12,0:07:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.48,0:07:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you've made up your mind,\Nlet's get ready to leave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.29,0:07:26.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.80,0:07:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.71,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And seriously,\N if Pegasus is gonna pick us up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.38,0:07:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we get to go to America for {\i1}free{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.45,0:07:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.31,0:07:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys are too much...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.61,0:07:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's go~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.62,0:07:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.16,0:07:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America, they said?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.61,0:07:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking a' Pegasus,\Nhe's the creator a' Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.08,0:07:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he {\i1}invited{\i0} those yahoos?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.23,0:07:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Industrial Illusions is a company well known for selling cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They must have a {\i1}ton{\i0} of rare cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.41,0:07:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.37,0:07:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Alrighty then!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.45,0:08:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Take all the rare cards\N you like, kiddies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wow, amazing~!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.64,0:08:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you, Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.93,0:08:09.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ain't fair, ain't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ain't cool that those bumpkins are gettin' all the rare cards to themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.97,0:08:15.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.26,0:08:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't stand by and let them hog all the cards to themselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.19,0:08:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We gotta get the \Nrare cards for ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.71,0:08:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But... how?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.89,0:08:25.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We plan {\i1}ahead{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:09:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By capturing the souls of countless Duelists and obtaining the power of the three God Cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.44,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the door has been opened.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Lend us your power, Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.11,0:09:16.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I cannot believe the nameless Pharaoh has obtained the power of {\i1}that{\i0} dragon...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our God has only just been awoken.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:28.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A great deal of offerings shall be required if we wish to keep its strength alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.33,0:09:30.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Pharaoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:32.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You shall not get\N in our way any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.04,0:09:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rafael!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.78,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you command.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.47,0:09:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll present the soul of the nameless Pharaoh to our God this time for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.93,0:09:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That alone shall not be suffice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we desire to fully revive our God,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.73,0:09:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we require the souls of as many talented Duelists as we can possibly obtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please let me handle taking the soul of Seto Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.24,0:09:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll be taking Katsuya Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat him to a bloody pulp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.95,0:10:04.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}then{\i0} I'll steal his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.24,0:10:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for the sake of that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.62,0:10:09.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why do {\i1}you{\i0} insist\N on sticking with Kaiba so much?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And {\i1}that{\i0} would be\N none of {\i1}your{\i0} business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.84,0:10:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.55,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you two give it a rest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.01,0:10:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We stand before Lord Dartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:24.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaving the nameless Pharaoh aside, we desire the soul of another powerful Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.01,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to head towards where Pegasus J. Crawford resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.02,0:10:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.14,0:10:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have already made arrangements for another person to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All you three need do is pick her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.85,0:10:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.37,0:10:49.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please hurry and get here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.48,0:10:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something terrible has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are..
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,NO~!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.34,0:11:25.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.37,0:11:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how long we're going to stay there for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.00,0:11:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.63,0:11:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never expected to return there in a way like {\i1}this{\i0}...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell should I bring with me to America!?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.40,0:11:58.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be out of the country for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.07,0:11:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.74,0:12:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And don't you go\N catching a cold, Shizuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Better not forget to bring this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.42,0:12:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Key of Illusion"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.42,0:12:22.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what the key card is this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.93,0:12:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Other Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.64,0:12:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.14,0:12:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's up, Partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.10,0:12:33.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you thinking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.96,0:12:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.42,0:12:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.39,0:12:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something is troubling you, but you're trying to hide it. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.11,0:12:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't keep {\b0}anything{\b1} from you, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.66,0:12:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.62,0:12:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm thinking about\Nhow to deal with the enemy this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.02,0:12:52.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just who are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's possible... that I already know who they are... in my lost memories, anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.75,0:12:59.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, there you go again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:05.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you'll not conceal\Nwhat's on your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.26,0:13:07.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, there's so much we don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.46,0:13:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.52,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess... I guess I have a bad feeling about all this!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something we're not\N aware of is approaching.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.65,0:13:17.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me really nervous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.86,0:13:18.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Partner...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.98,0:13:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...\NFor saying something strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.39,0:13:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright... let's hurry and get some rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.26,0:13:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good night, my other self.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.86,0:13:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Grandpa.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.20,0:13:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.82,0:13:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I learn any new information\N from Arthur,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.79,0:13:49.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be sure to inform you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.79,0:13:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.59,0:13:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.76,0:13:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.92,0:13:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll leave now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.72,0:13:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.96,0:14:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.92,0:14:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're going on that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rich people sure go all out on everything they do!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:13.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's Pegasus or Kaiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} is in America too, isn't he, Yugi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.05,0:14:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.72,0:14:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But with the Duel Monsters\Nappearing everywhere in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he's probably totally exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I like the sound of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.42,0:14:28.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must be Master Yugi Mutou.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.52,0:14:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.55,0:14:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.29,0:14:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll get your luggage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.05,0:14:40.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.09,0:14:46.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.22,0:14:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a reception room!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.19,0:14:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This plane is exclusively reserved just for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.69,0:14:51.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.41,0:14:54.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the best thing I've ever sat on!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.76,0:14:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Yugi, come and sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.80,0:14:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... give me a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.11,0:15:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.19,0:15:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.59,0:15:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.46,0:15:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off we go to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.17,0:15:41.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good! We succeeded!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.92,0:15:45.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're gonna go to America!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.39,0:15:47.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But should we stay inside the cockpit 'til arrival?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.05,0:15:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.46,0:15:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't get the rare cards\Nif they find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.99,0:15:57.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes~! It looks delicious~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.98,0:16:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,F-Freezing~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.69,0:16:02.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Endure it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.79,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is all for the rare cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.05,0:16:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll die~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.72,0:16:16.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell came up\N with this horrible plan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Endure it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.72,0:16:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.19,0:16:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.12,0:16:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a great plane!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.02,0:16:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.86,0:16:44.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please get into this car.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.09,0:16:46.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,EH~
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.65,0:16:48.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time it's a {\i1}limousine{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.76,0:16:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.62,0:16:51.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did we have a bag like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.55,0:16:53.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, whose bag is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.52,0:16:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.86,0:16:55.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.02,0:16:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe someone mistakenly took the wrong bag?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.57,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.19,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll handle it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.82,0:17:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,America~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.65,0:17:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rare cards~
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.82,0:17:19.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we announced earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.69,0:17:24.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever this current situation is, it has nothing to do with our Kaiba Corporation's Solid Vision!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.76,0:17:26.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just answer them like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:33.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is {\i1}happening{\i0}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.78,0:17:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this some kind of elaborate takeover plot being orchestrated by one of Kaiba Corporation's competitors?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.91,0:17:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has there been an answer from Industrial Illusions yet?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.41,0:17:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right. We haven't heard anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then try and contact them again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.83,0:17:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is a very important time for Kaiba Corporation and our plan to build Kaiba Land around the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.02,0:17:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.68,0:17:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.69,0:18:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's bought a huge amount of Kaiba Corporation's stocks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.96,0:18:01.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's just {\i1}no way{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.52,0:18:16.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How could {\i1}anyone{\i0} buy this many of our stocks without us finding out about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.28,0:18:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just {\i1}how{\i0} did they...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.69,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother... What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let them do us any more harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.79,0:18:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll find {\i1}anyone{\i0} who\N dares to get in my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:29.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll make them {\i1}regret{\i0} it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.72,0:18:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.99,0:18:38.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hi, Kaiba boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.92,0:18:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did you receive\N the message I sent you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.26,0:18:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is {\i1}your{\i0} doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.81,0:18:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was just a friendly greeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.39,0:18:53.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I take it you didn't like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.02,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.20,0:18:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're even more\N persistent than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.44,0:18:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're {\i1}still{\i0} planning to take over Kaiba Corporation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! Please don't make such a scary face!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This was merely a demonstration.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:07.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Demonstration{\i0}, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.62,0:19:08.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A little tease before our Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.76,0:19:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's been far too long since we last Dueled one another!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.85,0:19:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you accept this challenge?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.34,0:19:18.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell would come visit {\i1}you{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.67,0:19:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.47,0:19:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kaiba boy, you cannot simply ignore me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because if you do not come, I will sell all of the stocks I purchased from Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.94,0:19:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I were to do {\b0}that{\b1}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.81,0:19:32.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your company will nosedive!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.31,0:19:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And your dream will {\b0}fade away{\b1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You scumbag...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Still not going to come, Kaiba boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:41.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.24,0:19:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.53,0:19:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I invite you to the ever-so nostalgic Duelist Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.17,0:19:54.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll be waiting for you, Kaiba boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.84,0:19:57.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}After Battle City ended,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}my brother sealed away his cards in order to focus on the plan for Kaiba Land production.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.31,0:20:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now he has no choice but to go against his word...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:50.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Pegasus...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.18,0:20:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yugi is the only man I've truly lost to.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.49,0:21:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If you plan to\N stand in my way once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll beat you down until you {\b0}move{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.43,0:21:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.91,0:21:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pegasus may once again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.23,0:21:34.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be afraid, Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.94,0:21:37.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same strategy won't work on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.21,0:21:39.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.02,0:22:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.99,0:22:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.06,0:22:31.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.54,0:22:40.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.82,0:22:50.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.72,0:22:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.87,0:23:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.39,0:23:14.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.87,0:23:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We have been invited by Pegasus\Nto come to America.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.58,0:23:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, in order to fight that same Pegasus,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.12,0:23:28.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} is headed for Duelist Kingdom.
